data.description: Welcome to this spacious 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom pool home nestled on an impressive, nearly 1-acre lot in the desirable Wekiwa Hills community. The 4th bedroom is not included in the floorplan online for privacy reasons but there is in fact a 4th bedroom and it is the largest of the guest bedrooms. Privacy is paramount on this expansive property that is brimming with potential, waiting for you to add your personal touch. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by a cozy living room featuring a charming fireplace – a perfect spot to unwind during cooler evenings. Continuing through, you'll find the kitchen and family room, thoughtfully connected, allowing for comfortable daily living and easy entertaining. This home boasts a true split floorplan, ensuring privacy with the primary bedroom conveniently located off the living room. The remaining bedrooms and guest bathroom can be found on the opposite side of the home, providing ample space for family or guests. Step outside onto the enormous screened-in porch overlooking the sprawling backyard. The centerpiece of the backyard is the sizable pool, providing the perfect place to cool off in the summer. Additionally, there's no HOA! For outdoor enthusiasts, the popular Wekiwa Springs State Park is just a stone's throw away, spanning 7,000 acres and offering a plethora of activities. Explore miles of trails for hiking, biking, and horseback riding, or take to the water for canoeing and kayaking adventures. Conveniently located near a variety of shopping, entertainment, and dining options, this home offers the best of both worlds: a peaceful retreat and easy access to amenities. Don't miss out on this opportunity to create your own haven in the heart of Wekiwa Hills so schedule your private showing today!
